plot: Netero receives an order from the leaders of the world and prepares to eliminate the Ants. Colt and his fellow Ants are eager to learn more about Nen. Gon, Killua, and Kite battle a group of Ants in a one on one battle.

News about the Chimera Ants threat reach the Hunter Association and an expedition is assembled to exterminate them. Meanwhile, Kite, Gon and Killua are surrounded by a large number of enemies and must fight for their lives. Back at the nest, the other squadron leaders look for a way to awaken the Nen in their bodies just like Rammot did.—paulp1988
